-- Q-Cells Agrees on Early Loan Repayment with LDK Solar of China
-- Zoe Schneeweiss
-- 2010-09-20T05:55:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/q-cells-convertibles-surge-to-two-year-high-as-loan-will-be-repaid-early.html

          
          
             Q-Cells SE, a German photovoltaic
company, said it has reached an agreement with LDK Solar of
China to repay the loan extended to LDK Solar by Q-Cells in 2008
early and to adjust the existing solar wafer supply contract.  
 Q-Cells said the $224.9 million loan will be repaid by the 
end of 2011, the company said in a statement today.  
